{"tid":2037910,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[親自回應]蔡英文Facebook：強化對港人的協助，會請行政院提出 #香港人道援助行動專案","createTime":"2020-05-27T08:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T11:31:54.000Z","uid":109923,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53f73f9b80e1168b43cfe152992d63cfba1ad510","tid":2037910,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kweey6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kweey6.jpg&h=57c3a8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近來大家都很關心香港情勢的發展，我們跟世界上所有國家一樣，都非常期待香港對自由和人權的保護，不要受到進一步的侵蝕。我們嚴正呼籲：中國政府要 #懸崖勒馬，不要違反對香港「五十年不變」、「港人治港」的承諾，也應盡快讓香港社會恢復和平和對話。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港情勢惡化，香港的自治、人權進一步被壓縮，我們也要嚴正表達關心和聲明：我們會持續支持港人爭取民主自由的決心，因為香港的民主自由是區域和平穩定的重要因素。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港朋友，我們也一直在提供相關的協助。目前香港人民要來台灣相對已經是比較寬鬆，去年一整年，香港朋友來台居留的人數突破五千人，相較於前一年成長41%。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>關於強化對港人的協助，今天早上我和行政院 蘇貞昌 院長進行討論，會請行政院提出 #香港人道援助行動專案</strong>，由陸委會負責盤整資源，透過跨部會協調來進行，包括對港人的居留、安置、照顧，要在最短時間內提出完整、明確的規劃。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>之前有人質疑，調整 #香港澳門關係條例 是切割，這完全是錯誤解讀。</strong>我也要再次強調，無論制度怎麼調整，我們 #照顧香港人民的決心不變。"},{"pid":"9691562ec6fced0ec3c6d4fa9d8d1d6e9c810091","tid":2037910,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T08:55:45.000Z","msg":"中國口交部:  干預國家內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77367aaaf965319a6daf13d5bddf75e8455fd28f","tid":2037910,"uid":253600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"幫你貼link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/photos/a.390960786064/10156758682791065/?type=3&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaiingwen%2Fphotos%2Fa.390960786064%2F10156758682791065%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26__tn__%3D-R&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=c0be78b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/photos/a.390960786064/10156758682791065/?type=3&amp;__tn__=-R</a>"},{"pid":"796646bdfa62661fc87405589a11d4c0abd6148c","tid":2037910,"uid":105872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07dfc3261a11d413d1e805e77843aa09c13e128f","tid":2037910,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"全球搶真香港人行動由台灣打響第一槍"},{"pid":"c4b593de823148106758f1205ddfd44ef6a22ed2","tid":2037910,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f365e91557b17ddb852184ab2bfdddf7ec0b88","tid":2037910,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf05769f803b32fc1567ded48c742c0b30c1c708","tid":2037910,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:19:41.000Z","msg":"制裁基本上準備就緒"},{"pid":"602a0414a67d68e6a54e54726139d78b9fd6c88a","tid":2037910,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"台灣咁高調出聲扮明侵侵黎真"}]}